1 Absolute LF-MS on unfertilised egg

Comparing abs protein eggs (LF-MS) and relative protein eggs (TMTcPro-MS). The data are normalized using Theil-Sen estimator which is robust against outliers.

I will then compare to relative proteomics (TMTc) and RNA (salmon counts)

  1. Compare egg absolute vs relative
  2. Compare egg protein vs RNA
